{
  "stem": "9898.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She threw him out a 20, 20 coin-- 20, 20 golden dollars.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he gave her the bottle of water.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was urine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was just to tell you how-- what they thought about us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the morning, around 5:30, 6 o'clock, we arrived at a regular station.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were sure that we were going to Treblinka, just like any other person-- like any other transport.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We came, and they opened the door.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a railroad station.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, the first thing, the German soldiers gave us water to drink.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have any idea what is water, how water tastes when you're dying from thirst?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I myself probably drank half a bucket.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And everybody else did the same thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we left-- from 200 people, only 60-- 50 or 60 survived.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The rest were dead.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we came out, there were soldiers, Polish soldiers, who were working-- helping the Germans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We asked them, where are we?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They said, you are in Lublin, Station Lublin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you are going all to Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, we knew what Majdanek was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was a killer camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, first of all, they treated there the people worse than animals.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They worked them to death.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they gassed them and burned them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The commanding officer in Lublin was Goth-- Goeth-- G-O-T-Z-E, Gotze.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Polish government caught him after the war and then hanged him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They hanged him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were in rows of 12-- old men, young men, children, woman, mixed-- in front of a huge gate.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was in the fourth or fifth row from the left side now.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And a yard, a couple of yards from us was a SS major standing there, giving orders to open the doors, to start to leave to, to Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
